Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Goleta Beach
Description: One of my favorite places to walk and hang out with friends to talk!

Name: Storke Tower
Description: One of the many awesome landmarks in Santa Barbara. Conveniently located on UCSB campus as well.

Name: Old Mission Santa Barbara
Description: A spanish mission located in Santa Barbara that offers a nice little history about the area! Offers a neat museum viewing as well.

Name: Santa Barbara Harbor
Description: A great place to visit for a variety of aquatic activities, including: sailing, kayaking, paddle boarding, scuba diving, etc. Nice for a vacation spot.

Name: Gaviota Vista Viewpoint
Description: A beautiful place to sightsee or take one of many hiking trails to visit different ecosystems!
